                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 312.11/6957.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Consul <persName type="from">Garrett</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Laredo</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-11-22">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 22, 1915</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Neither Silliman nor Belt here. Your November 22 to Silliman forwarded to him at
                    Saltillo. General Carranza here. If Department so instructs, will take matters
                    up with him and try to secure needed relief for Los Mochis.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Garrett.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
